;; ========================================================================
;;
;; Phase 0b: Run baseline — Sections A, B, G must pass (uncommented)
;;           Sections C, D, E, F are aspirational (commented out)
;;           Catalog failures as BUG annotations with hypotheses
;;
;; Phase 0a (= wiring): Driven by Phase 0b failures.
;;           Expect: Section A fully passing, Section C partially.
;;
;; Phase 0d (adversarial): Written AFTER acceptance is clean.
;;           Separate file: benchmarks/comparative/punify-adversarial.prologos
;;
;; Phase 0c (baseline): bench-ab.rkt on adversarial, 15+ runs.
;;
;; Part 2 phases (1-9): Cell-tree architecture.
;;           Each phase: run this file, confirm no regressions.
;;           Aspirational sections uncommented as capabilities land.
